built in the last 10 years.

304
00:20:18,125 --> 00:20:20,833
- Beans and what not! So...

305
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,958
- Don't try to fool the people with that.

306
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,375
Park your vehicle
to the side, bro!

307
00:20:25,416 --> 00:20:27,541
