358
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:52,291
I had told her before
the wedding, right?

359
00:22:52,333 --> 00:22:54,125
- I was just asking... Okay.

360
00:22:54,291 --> 00:22:56,000
- Anyway, call me
after the meeting.

361
00:22:56,166 --> 00:22:57,458
- Okay, then.
- Okay.

