00:24:08,791 --> 00:24:09,833
Seven.

394
00:24:09,875 --> 00:24:11,583
- And date of missing?

395
00:24:13,666 --> 00:24:14,791
3 years back.

396
00:24:15,375 --> 00:24:16,750
March 20th,

397
00:24:17,291 --> 00:24:18,541
2021.

398
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:23,583
- So how long did you follow up
