430
00:26:09,791 --> 00:26:11,541
[phone rings]
- Yes.

431
00:26:11,541 --> 00:26:13,541
And a bit of theatre
and travel in between.

432
00:26:13,666 --> 00:26:15,500
She has come here
leaving all that behind.

433
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:17,375
She is a perfect
match for Ajayettan.

434
00:26:17,416 --> 00:26:20,791
