what they shouldn't do, Mohanetta?

437
00:26:27,625 --> 00:26:29,333
- Hmm. Okay.

438
00:26:29,541 --> 00:26:30,583
- Yes.

439
00:26:30,583 --> 00:26:31,916
11th block, right?

440
00:26:32,041 --> 00:26:34,208
