444
00:26:41,416 --> 00:26:42,500
Let's go visit the place.

445
00:26:42,500 --> 00:26:43,541
It was Shaiju who called.

446
00:26:43,541 --> 00:26:44,875
He is at the spot now.

447
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:45,791
Where is it?

448
00:26:45,833 --> 00:26:48,125
