1695
01:54:07,375 --> 01:54:09,083
It's a painkiller
overdose, Doctor.

1696
01:54:09,458 --> 01:54:12,708
Taking one or two more tablets than
necessary is called an overdose,

1697
01:54:12,750 --> 01:54:14,916
